response.overview: A Film written and directed by Ethan Hausauer and Zach Zawadzki made about their brave and courageous Advanced Placement  United States History (apush) Teacher Mr. Stonebraker. Who stood up against the menacing Matthew Wagner and corrupt college board.  This Film was made through East Aurora High School Film Academy.
response.tagline: He was more than a Teacher
response.title: Rockcrusher
